<li><strong>Marketing is an afterthought</strong> (needs integrations)</li>
<li>You'll end up paying for other tools to fill gaps</li>
<li>Email capabilities basic compared to HubSpot</li>
<li>Reporting not as deep as HubSpot</li>
<li>Smaller ecosystem (400 vs 1,000+ integrations)</li>
<li>Per-user pricing gets expensive with large teams</li>
<li>No landing pages or forms built-in</li>
</ul>
</div>
